8. Be2 e5 $5 $146 {This move, although a bit unusual, is the best way to
equalize the game.} (8... Bb4 {This is the most popular move.} 9. f3 d5 10. a3
Bxc3 $6 11. Qxc3 dxe4 {Black has great statistics where almost all the games
have been won by Black, but in reality, the position is better for White.} 12.
