active counterplay, so I'm not recommending this line.} (11. exd5 cxd5 12. Be3
(12. Bf4 {Firouzja - Mastrovasilis,D Catez 2021} Bb7 13. O-O-O Bc5 14. f3 O-O
$11) 12... h6 13. g4 Rg8 $13) 11... Bb7 (11... Bb4 12. Bd2 O-O 13. f3 $14 {
