) 16... Ng6 {White doesn't have enough resources to overpower Black on the
kingside.}) 14... f5 {Limiting the activity of White's light-squared bishop.}
15. Kh1 (15. c3 bxc3 16. bxc3 Nb4 17. Be3 Nxd3 18. Qxd3 Bd7 19. Bd4 Bxb5 20.
Qxb5 Qc7 21. Qe2 Ra6 $11) 15... Bd7 16. a4 Qd8 17. c3 {Niemann - Pichot, chess.
com rapid 2022} d4 $5 18. cxb4 Nxb4 19. Bc4 Qb6 20. Bd2 Nd5 $13) (7. Be3 a6 (
7... Be7 {Trying to avoid playing the move a7-a6 can put Black in an
unpleasant position.} 8. f4 d6 9. Qd2 $5 $36) 8. a3 (8. Qd2 {This is a strange
