14. axb4 Bxb4 $132) (9. Qd2 b5 10. Nxc6 dxc6 11. f4 Bb7 12. e5 Rd8 13. Qc1 (13.
Bd3 Ng4 $36) 13... Nd7 14. O-O c5 $132) 9... O-O (9... d6 {This prevents e4-e5
but after} 10. g4 $36 {Even though White lost a tempo wwith a2-a3, this
